Nmap <span class="k">done</span>: 1 IP address <span class="o">(</span>1 host up<span class="o">)</span> scanned <span class="k">in </span>9.83 seconds
</code></pre></div></div>
<p>In the output we can see that port 22 SSH is filtered, it is possible that certain firewall rules may be blocking incoming traffic, the only port that‚Äôs open is 80 HTTP.</p>

